WEBVTT

00:03:26.634 --> 00:03:30.034
to join rescue teams
during times of active crisis.

00:03:30.563 --> 00:03:35.227
This is why my wife and I and friends
co-founded "Humanity Crew."

00:03:36.193 --> 00:03:38.321
One of the few aid
organizations in the world

00:03:38.345 --> 00:03:40.964
that specializes in providing
psychosocial aid

00:03:40.988 --> 00:03:43.569
and first-response
mental health interventions

00:03:43.593 --> 00:03:46.228
to refugees and displaced populations.

00:03:46.252 --> 00:03:49.006
To provide them
with a suitable intervention,

00:03:49.030 --> 00:03:52.458
we create the four-step approach,
a psychosocial work plan

00:03:52.482 --> 00:03:55.918
that follows the refugees
on each step of their journey.

00:03:56.371 --> 00:04:00.601
Starting inside the sea,
on the rescue boats,